[SLR-25] GHD equipment must be monitored and operated safely.
[A-20] Entities involved in GHD communicate and expect coordination.""";
    stampo:code "LS-22";
    stampo:external-code "1246" .
  
  <http://onto.fel.cvut.cz/ontologies/stpa-analysis/SMS_-_Ground_Handling_Inspection/LossScenario--LS-46>
    dcterms:description """Airport Management does not provide the engages action
