    dcterms:description """Airport Safety Manager does provide the assign inspection action when rising trend of GHD incidents are recorded
- assign inspection is not received by Safety inspector when rising trend of GHD incidents are recorded. Safety Manager used uncommon task assignment method, which was not actively used by employee.

[SLR-13] Management must be performed on unified platform and with unified terminology.
[A-9] Safety can be measured and managed on various platforms.  .""";
    stampo:code "LS-25";
